           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@   업무처리SUB
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3300-PROCESS-SUB-RTN.

           PERFORM  S3310-DATA-MOVE-RTN
              THRU  S3310-DATA-MOVE-EXT

      ****************************************
      *@ 통화한도，통화잔액
      *@  B/S 　잔액（매매기준적용）
      *@ 명목액기준한도,명목액기준잔액 = 0 이면 SKIP처리     *
      ****************************************
           IF  RJL0025-CRNCY-CLAM        =  ZERO AND
               RJL0025-CRNCY-BAL         =  ZERO AND
               RJL0025-BS-BASE-BAL       =  ZERO AND
               RJL0025-TTL-AMT-BASE-CLAM =  ZERO AND
               RJL0025-TTL-AMT-BASE-BAL  =  ZERO
           THEN
               ADD  CO-NUM-1    TO  WK-SKIP-ZERO-CNT
           ELSE
               PERFORM  S3320-DATA-WRITE-RTN
                  THRU  S3320-DATA-WRITE-EXT
           END-IF

           .
       S3300-PROCESS-SUB-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@   DATA MOVE:기업계좌　데이타　  MOVE
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3310-DATA-MOVE-RTN.

           INITIALIZE    OT-REC

      *    그룹회사코드
           MOVE  WK-H-I-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO  RJL0025-GROUP-CO-CD

      *    계좌번호
           MOVE  WK-H-O-ACNO
             TO  RJL0025-ACNO

      *    기준일
           MOVE  WK-H-I-BASE-DD
             TO  RJL0025-BASE-DD

      *    기준년월
           MOVE  WK-H-I-BASE-YM
             TO  RJL0025-BASE-YM

      *@   계좌중복일련번호 = 계좌번호가 같을 경우
      *@                        계좌중복일련번호 증가
           IF  WK-H-O-ACNO = WK-ACNO-CHECK
           THEN
                 ADD  CO-NUM-1     TO  WK-SEQ
                MOVE  WK-SEQ
                  TO  RJL0025-ACN-DUP-SERNO
           ELSE
                MOVE  CO-NUM-1     TO  WK-SEQ
                MOVE  WK-SEQ
                  TO  RJL0025-ACN-DUP-SERNO
           END-IF

      *    고객식별자
           MOVE  WK-H-O-CTCR-CUST-ID
             TO  RJL0025-CUST-IDNFR

      *    고객관리번호
           MOVE  WK-H-O-CTCR-CUST-MGT-NO
             TO  RJL0025-CUST-MGT-NO

      *    해외현지법인여부
           MOVE  CO-CHA-0
             TO  RJL0025-OVSES-LCAL-COPR-YN

      *@  고객식별자로　법인고객식별자(차주고객식별자) 조회
           PERFORM  S3310-KAABPCB-SELECT-RTN
              THRU  S3310-KAABPCB-SELECT-EXT

      *@   차주고객식별자
           MOVE  WK-COPR-CUST-IDNFR
             TO  RJL0025-BRWR-CUST-IDNFR

      *    관리부점코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O-MGT-BRNCD
             TO  RJL0025-MGT-BRNCD

      *    계좌적용구분　세팅（순수개인이면　계좌적용구분＝＇７＇）
           PERFORM  S3310-KAABPDC-SELECT-RTN
              THRU  S3310-KAABPDC-SELECT-EXT

      *    한도계좌여부
           MOVE  WK-H-O-LIMT-ACN-YN
             TO  RJL0025-LIMT-ACN-YN

      *    상품대분류코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O-PRDCT-LAG-CLSFI-CD
             TO  RJL0025-PRDCT-LAG-CLSFI-CD

      *    상품중분류코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O-PRDCT-MEDM-CLSFI-CD
             TO  RJL0025-PRDCT-MEDM-CLSFI-CD

      *    상품템플릿코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O-PRDCT-TMPLT-CD
             TO  RJL0025-PRDCT-TMPLT-CD

      *@ 상품번호
      *@  - 064,065,066은　개별구분에　따라　환산율　다르게　적용
      *@  -상품대분류코드＝２５는　그대로　사용
           EVALUATE  WK-H-O-GUBN
               WHEN  '063'
                     MOVE  WK-H-O-PRDCT-NO
                       TO  RJL0025-PRDCT-NO
               WHEN  '064'
               WHEN  '065'
               WHEN  '066'
                     IF  RJL0025-PRDCT-LAG-CLSFI-CD = '25'
                     THEN
                         MOVE  WK-H-O-PRDCT-NO
                           TO  RJL0025-PRDCT-NO
                     ELSE
      *                 잔액유형구분3 + 상품번호2
                         MOVE  CO-CHA-0
                           TO  RJL0025-PRDCT-NO(1:1)
                         MOVE  WK-H-O-JAN-GUBN(3:2)
                           TO  RJL0025-PRDCT-NO(2:2)
                         MOVE  WK-H-O-PRDCT-NO(4:2)
                           TO  RJL0025-PRDCT-NO(4:2)
                     END-IF
               WHEN  OTHER
                     MOVE  WK-H-O-PRDCT-NO
                       TO  RJL0025-PRDCT-NO
           END-EVALUATE

      *-------------------------------------------------------------
      *@대외선박선수금환급보증（확정／미확정）구분　요청（신병기대리）
      *@ - AS-IS는　계정과목코드로　확정／미확정　구분
      *@ - TO-BE는　상품정보통합으로　확정／미확정　잔액유형　으로구분
      *@ -상품정보 25-59-H34-00001/00002-> A0001/A0002
      *@ -           25-63-H34-00001/00002-> A0001/A0002
      *@ -잔액유형 B001 :대출잔액(선박선수금확정잔액)
      *@ -           B002 :선박선수금미확정잔액
      *@ 상품정보＝상품대＋상품중＋템플릿＋상품번호

           INITIALIZE    WK-PRDCT-CD

           STRING WK-H-O-PRDCT-LAG-CLSFI-CD
                  WK-H-O-PRDCT-MEDM-CLSFI-CD
                  WK-H-O-PRDCT-TMPLT-CD
                  WK-H-O-PRDCT-NO
           DELIMITED BY SIZE INTO  WK-PRDCT-CD

           IF ( WK-PRDCT-CD  = '2559H3400001' OR
                WK-PRDCT-CD  = '2559H3400002' OR
                WK-PRDCT-CD  = '2563H3400001' OR
                WK-PRDCT-CD  = '2563H3400002' ) AND
                WK-H-O-JAN-GUBN  = 'B002'
           THEN
      *        A +상품번호４
               STRING CO-CHA-A
                      WK-H-O-PRDCT-NO(2:4)
               DELIMITED BY SIZE INTO  RJL0025-PRDCT-NO
           END-IF
      *-------------------------------------------------------------

      *    시작년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-O-PRDCT-C-CRETN-YMD
             TO  RJL0025-START-YMD

      *@   수입개설기본／수입무신용장기본　만기년월일　추출
      *@   여신구분＝０６５　수입이면　만기년월일　추출
           IF  WK-H-O-GUBN = '065'
           THEN
                PERFORM  S3310-KFE0005-SELECT-RTN
                   THRU  S3310-KFE0005-SELECT-EXT
           END-IF

      *   만기년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-O-PRDCT-C-EXPIR-YMD
             TO  RJL0025-EXPIR-YMD

      *    종료년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-O-PRDCT-C-DSCRD-YMD
             TO  RJL0025-END-YMD

      *    상품계약상태구분
           MOVE  WK-H-O-PRDCT-C-STUS-DSTCD
             TO  RJL0025-PRDCT-C-STUS-DSTCD

      *    통화코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O-CNCYCD
             TO  RJL0025-CNCYCD

      *    통화한도＝잔액
           MOVE  WK-H-O-CNPR
             TO  RJL0025-CRNCY-CLAM

      *    통화잔액＝잔액
           MOVE  WK-H-O-CNPR
             TO  RJL0025-CRNCY-BAL

      *계약한도（계좌한도）
      *모계좌　존재하면　한도계좌여부＝＇１＇，통화한도＝０으로
           PERFORM  S3310-KHC0007-SELECT-RTN
              THRU  S3310-KHC0007-SELECT-EXT

      * 통화코드가　원화일때
           IF  WK-H-O-CNCYCD = CO-CHA-KRW
           THEN
      *        BS기준잔액
               MOVE  RJL0025-CRNCY-BAL
                 TO  RJL0025-BS-BASE-BAL

      *        명목액기준한도
               MOVE  RJL0025-CRNCY-CLAM
                 TO  RJL0025-TTL-AMT-BASE-CLAM

      *        명목액기준잔액
               MOVE  RJL0025-CRNCY-BAL
                 TO  RJL0025-TTL-AMT-BASE-BAL
           ELSE
      *통화별　원화환산금액 CALCURATER
               PERFORM  S3312-BJLTGEX-CALL-RTN
                  THRU  S3312-BJLTGEX-CALL-EXT
           END-IF

      *    TE한도환산금액
           MOVE  ZERO
             TO  RJL0025-TE-LIMT-AUC

      *    TE잔액환산금액
           MOVE  ZERO
             TO  RJL0025-TE-BAL-AUC

      *    CP한도환산금액
           MOVE  ZERO
             TO  RJL0025-INLS-GRCR-LIMT-AUC

      *    CP잔액환산금액
           MOVE  ZERO
             TO  RJL0025-INLS-GRCR-BAL-AUC

      *    CA담보제외금액
           MOVE  ZERO
             TO  RJL0025-CA-SCURTY-ECLUD-AMT

      *    CA담보환산금액
           MOVE  ZERO
             TO  RJL0025-CA-SCURTY-AUC

      *   관련테이블명
           MOVE  WK-H-O-TABLE-NM
             TO  RJL0025-RELATD-TBL-NAME

      *   과목코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O-GUBN
             TO  RJL0025-SBJCT-CD

      *   시스템최종처리일시
           MOVE  BICOM-TRAN-BASE-YMS
             TO  RJL0025-SYS-LAST-PRCSS-YMS

      *   시스템최종사용자번호
           MOVE  BICOM-USER-EMPID
             TO  RJL0025-SYS-LAST-UNO

      *계좌중복여부　확인- SEQ COUNT 증가여부　확인
           MOVE  WK-H-O-ACNO
             TO  WK-ACNO-CHECK
           .
       S3310-DATA-MOVE-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  계좌적용구분－순수개인　구분
      *@  - BJLD25H에서　순수개인을　분류　할수　없어서　여기서　처리
      *@  - WHY? : THKJL0015에는　순수개인정보가　없어서　처리　못함
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3310-KAABPDC-SELECT-RTN.

      *   거래자구분＝＇０１＇－－＞　개인　AS-IS그대로이행
      *   세부고객유형분류구분＝＇１１＇－－＞　개인　TO-BE기준
      *   세부고객유형분류구분으로　개인구분이　더　정확함

           INITIALIZE    WK-DTALS-CPC-DSTCD

           EXEC SQL
             SELECT  VALUE(세부고객유형분류구분,'00')
               INTO  :WK-DTALS-CPC-DSTCD
               FROM  DB2DBA.THKAABPDC
              WHERE  그룹회사코드    = :WK-H-I-GROUP-CO-CD
                AND  고객식별자      = :WK-H-O-CTCR-CUST-ID
                AND  고객관리번호    = :WK-H-O-CTCR-CUST-MGT-NO
           END-EXEC

           EVALUATE  SQLCODE
               WHEN  CO-OK
      *             세부고객유형분류구분＝＇１１＇－－＞　개인
                     IF  WK-DTALS-CPC-DSTCD = CO-CHA-11
                     THEN
      *                 계좌적용구분
                         MOVE  CO-CHA-7  TO  RJL0025-ACN-APLY-DSTCD
                     ELSE
      *                 계좌적용구분
                         MOVE  CO-CHA-0  TO  RJL0025-ACN-APLY-DSTCD
                     END-IF
               WHEN  CO-NOT-FOUND
      *                 계좌적용구분
                         MOVE  CO-CHA-0  TO  RJL0025-ACN-APLY-DSTCD
               WHEN  OTHER
                     MOVE 'KAABPDC'    TO  XZUGEROR-I-TBL-ID
                     MOVE 'SELECT'     TO  XZUGEROR-I-FUNC-CD
                     MOVE  SQLCODE     TO  XZUGEROR-I-SQL-CD
                     MOVE 'SELECT S3310시오류가발생했습니다'
                                       TO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                     #ERROR  CO-EBM05001 CO-UBM05001 CO-STAT-ERROR
                     #OKEXIT CO-CHA-08
           END-EVALUATE
           .
       S3310-KAABPDC-SELECT-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@   수입개설기본／수입무신용장기본　만기년월일　추출
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3310-KFE0005-SELECT-RTN.

           INITIALIZE    WK-H-O-PRDCT-C-EXPIR-YMD

           EXEC SQL
             SELECT  VALUE("BL만기년월일",'00010101')
               INTO  :WK-H-O-PRDCT-C-EXPIR-YMD
               FROM  DB2DBA.THKFE0005
              WHERE  그룹회사코드 = :WK-H-I-GROUP-CO-CD
                AND  계좌번호     = :WK-H-O-ACNO
                AND  "BL일련번호" = (SELECT  MAX("BL일련번호")
                                         FROM  DB2DBA.THKFE0005
                                        WHERE 그룹회사코드
                                                 = :WK-H-I-GROUP-CO-CD
                                          AND 계좌번호
                                                 = :WK-H-O-ACNO
                                      )
           END-EXEC

           EVALUATE  SQLCODE
               WHEN  CO-OK
                     CONTINUE
               WHEN  CO-NOT-FOUND
                     MOVE '00010101'   TO  WK-H-O-PRDCT-C-EXPIR-YMD
               WHEN  OTHER
                     MOVE 'KFE0005'    TO  XZUGEROR-I-TBL-ID
                     MOVE 'SELECT'     TO  XZUGEROR-I-FUNC-CD
                     MOVE  SQLCODE     TO  XZUGEROR-I-SQL-CD
                     MOVE 'SELECT S3320시오류가발생했습니다'
                                       TO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                     #ERROR  CO-EBM05001 CO-UBM05001 CO-STAT-ERROR
                     #OKEXIT CO-CHA-08
           END-EVALUATE
           .
       S3310-KFE0005-SELECT-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  여신이개인으로분류된것중개인사업자정보가있는지확인
      *@  고객식별자로　법인고객식별자(차주고객식별자) 조회
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3310-KAABPCB-SELECT-RTN.

      *@   고객정보 초기화
           INITIALIZE    WK-COPR-CUST-IDNFR

      *@   고객고유번호구분= 02:사업자등록번호의
      *@                      법인고객식별자조회
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT  B.법인고객식별자
               INTO :WK-COPR-CUST-IDNFR
               FROM  DB2DBA.THKAABPCB A
                    ,DB2DBA.THKAABPCO B
              WHERE  A.그룹회사코드     = B.그룹회사코드
                AND  A.고객식별자       = B.고객식별자
                AND  A.그룹회사코드     = :WK-H-I-GROUP-CO-CD
                AND  A.고객식별자       = :WK-H-O-CTCR-CUST-ID
                AND  A.고객고유번호구분 = '02'
               WITH  UR
           END-EXEC

      *@   SQLCODE CHECK

           EVALUATE  SQLCODE
               WHEN  CO-OK
      *@법인사업자(THKAABPCO) 법인고객식별자조회
                     CONTINUE
               WHEN  CO-NOT-FOUND
      *@법인사업자(THKAABPCB)외의　고객고유번호조회
                     MOVE  WK-H-O-CTCR-CUST-ID
                       TO  WK-COPR-CUST-IDNFR
               WHEN  OTHER
                     MOVE 'KAABPCB'    TO  XZUGEROR-I-TBL-ID
                     MOVE 'SELECT'     TO  XZUGEROR-I-FUNC-CD
                     MOVE  SQLCODE     TO  XZUGEROR-I-SQL-CD
                     MOVE 'SELECT S3310시오류가발생했습니다'
                                       TO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                     #ERROR  CO-EBM05001 CO-UBM05001 CO-STAT-ERROR
                     #OKEXIT CO-CHA-08
           END-EVALUATE
           .
       S3310-KAABPCB-SELECT-EXT.
           EXIT.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  통화별원화환산금액 CALCURATER
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3312-BJLTGEX-CALL-RTN.

           INITIALIZE    XBJLTGEX-CA

      *    처리구분(1:통화별환산2:외환매매익　역환산)
           MOVE  CO-CHA-1
             TO  XBJLTGEX-I-GBCD

      *    유효년월일－기준년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-I-BASE-YMD
             TO  XBJLTGEX-I-BASE-YMD

      *    통화코드
           MOVE  RJL0025-CNCYCD
             TO  XBJLTGEX-I-CNCYCD

      *    통화한도금액
           MOVE  RJL0025-CRNCY-CLAM
             TO  XBJLTGEX-I-CRNCY-CLAM

      *    통화기준잔액
